ption><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 08:45:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/nato-type-southeast-asian-security-group-not-feasible-philippines-minister-says-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国对更多婴儿的最新呼声可能会被置若罔闻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-latest-cry-more-babies-may-fall-deaf-ears-2024-11-05/</link><description>人口统计学家表示，上周制定的政策对法国和瑞典等国家很有帮助，但在东亚却没有起到作用，很可能是由于性别不平等程度较高。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 08:04:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-latest-cry-more-babies-may-fall-deaf-ears-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>施罗德因大额客户退出而受到打击，股价下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/schroders-quarterly-flows-hit-by-china-market-volatility-2024-11-05/</link><description>施罗德周二报告称，第三季度资金流出逊于预期，而且即将失去更多大客户委托，这一令人沮丧的最新消息导致该公司股价在新任首席执行官理查德·奥德菲尔德(Richard Oldfield)上任几天前暴跌。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 07:31:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/schroders-quarterly-flows-hit-by-china-market-volatility-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国与欧洲混乱的电动汽车争端使贸易紧张局势得到控制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-messy-ev-dispute-with-europe-keeps-trade-tensions-check-2024-11-05/</link><description>尽管电动汽车贸易谈判陷入僵局，但对中国与其他主要出口国之间关税战扩大的担忧使得世界第二大经济体与欧盟之间的外交保持活力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 06:58:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-messy-ev-dispute-with-europe-keeps-trade-tensions-check-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>两名中国公民在巴基斯坦遭枪击受伤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/two-chinese-nationals-injured-after-being-shot-pakistans-karachi-authorities-say-2024-11-05/</link><description>周二，一名保安在巴基斯坦商业中心卡拉奇的一家服装厂开枪，造成两名中国公民受伤，这是一系列袭击事件中的最新一起，促使北京要求为其公民提供更好的安全保障。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 06:41:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/two-chinese-nationals-injured-after-being-shot-pakistans-karachi-authorities-say-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲第三季度财报半期：投资者奖励好消息，但对中国感到担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/q3-half-time-europe-investors-reward-beats-fret-about-china-2024-11-05/</link><description>欧洲第三季度盈利大多超出了市场的低预期，投资者的回报比多年来更加丰厚，尽管中国需求疲软令人谨慎。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 06:15:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/q3-half-time-europe-investors-reward-beats-fret-about-china-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国警告年轻士兵不要网上约会、赌博</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-warns-young-soldiers-against-online-dating-gambling-2024-11-05/</link><description>海军表示，不得在网上暴露军人身份。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 04:01:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-warns-young-soldiers-against-online-dating-gambling-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>李克强表示，中国必须进一步开放，对抗日益抬头的单边主义</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-must-open-up-further-combat-rising-unilateralism-premier-says-2024-11-05/</link><description>中国总理李强周二表示，中国将升级自贸区，并与其他国家探讨投资协定，并补充说，开放是对抗全球单边主义抬头的“必须”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 03:14:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-must-open-up-further-combat-rising-unilateralism-premier-says-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国批准摩根士丹利设立本土期货业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-gives-morgan-stanley-approval-launch-local-futures-unit-2024-11-05/</link><description>摩根士丹利已获得最终批准，通过新成立的子公司在中国开展期货业务，成为美国第二大进入世界第二大经济体衍生品市场的公司。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 02:54:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-gives-morgan-stanley-approval-launch-local-futures-unit-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>财新PMI显示，随着形势改善，中国服务业活动有所回升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-services-activity-picks-up-conditions-improve-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-11-05/</link><description>周二的一项私营部门调查显示，早期迹象表明北京的大规模刺激措施正在帮助改善商业环境，中国10月份的服务业活动以三个月来最快的速度扩张。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 01:50:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-services-activity-picks-up-conditions-improve-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普警告称，如果当选，他将就芬太尼对墨西哥和中国征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-says-he-will-put-tariff-mexico-stop-flow-fentanyl-into-us-2024-11-05/</link><description>共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普周一警告称，如果当选，他将以关税惩罚墨西哥和中国，除非两国政府采取行动阻止芬太尼流入美国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 01:30:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-says-he-will-put-tariff-mexico-stop-flow-fentanyl-into-us-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>高管表示，中国公司看好古巴太阳能发电</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinese-company-bullish-cuban-solar-drive-executive-says-2024-11-04/</link><description>向古巴销售太阳能技术的杭州多佳科技公司称，古巴大力发展太阳能发电的计划对两国来说是双赢，并大力宣传中国的制造业实力和古巴阳光明媚的气候。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 22:43:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinese-company-bullish-cuban-solar-drive-executive-says-2024-11-04/</guid></item></channel></rss>